Thursday, August 3, 1995

MERIT DOCKET

95-741. State ex rel. Mayville v. Shoemaker. Franklin County.

Appeal from the Court of Appeals for Franklin County, No. 94APD09-1398. On motion to dismiss. The judgment of the court of appeals is affirmed, and we note that this cause is moot.

Moyer, C.J., Douglas, Wright, Resnick and F.E. Sweeney, JJ., concur. Pfeifer, J., would affirm on Proposition of Law No. I only. Cook, J., would grant the motion to dismiss.
